  "prompt": "What do Indian IT companies like Infosys and Tech Mahindra do?",
  "response": "Indian IT companies like Infosys and Tech Mahindra provide a wide range of services in the information technology sector. Here\u2019s an overview of what these companies typically do:\n\n### Infosys\n1. **IT Services and Consulting**: Infosys offers end-to-end services in IT consulting, software development, system integration, and application development and maintenance.\n\n2. **Digital Transformation**: They provide services that help businesses transition to digital platforms, utilizing technologies like cloud computing, artificial intelligence, and the Internet of Things (IoT).\n\n3. **Business Process Management (BPM)**: Infosys assists businesses in optimizing their processes through automation and analytics, enhancing productivity and efficiency.\n\n4. **Engineering and Product Development**: They work on various aspects of product engineering, including design, testing, and lifecycle management.\n\n5. **Big Data and Analytics**: Infosys offers data management and analytics services to help businesses gain insights and make data-driven decisions.\n\n6. **Cybersecurity**: They provide cybersecurity solutions to protect businesses against threats and ensure data privacy and compliance.\n\n### Tech Mahindra\n1. **Telecom Solutions**: Tech Mahindra has a strong focus on telecom, providing network solutions, systems integration, and consulting services to telecommunications companies.\n\n2. **IT Services and Outsourcing**: They offer IT outsourcing services, including application development, infrastructure management, and customer support.\n\n3. **Enterprise Business Solutions**: Tech Mahindra provides ERP solutions, CRM, and supply chain management services to improve business processes.\n\n4. **Digital Transformation**: Like Infosys, Tech Mahindra aids businesses in migrating to digital operations, utilizing technologies such as cloud services, AI, and IoT.\n\n5. **Consulting and Integration Services**: They offer strategic consulting, integration, and managed services to optimize IT infrastructure and operations.\n\n6. **Healthcare and Lifesciences**: Tech Mahindra delivers services tailored to healthcare, including patient care solutions, telemedicine platforms, and regulatory compliance.\n\nBoth companies leverage their expertise in technology to serve global clients across various industries, including finance, healthcare, manufacturing, and retail, aiming to drive innovation and business growth.",
